SPDX-Depends: Description of dependencies
  The psmisc package contains utilities that use the proc file system, for
  example fuser, to identify processes that use the apt and dpkg lock files.
  .
  Package python3-systemd provides Python wrappers for systemd to, for example,
  log messages to the journal.
  .
  The rsync package provides for fast file copying, for example for backing up
  data.
Package: kz
Version: 4.2.1
Architecture: all
Depends: psmisc, python3-systemd, rsync
Maintainer: Karel Zimmer <info@karelzimmer.nl>
Homepage: https://karelzimmer.nl
Description: Installation and management scripts by Karel Zimmer
  Package kz contains scripts for installing and managing Debian and
  Debian-based systems such as Ubuntu.
  .
  For how to use this package see Checklist installation.
  Checklist installation can be found on the site https://karelzimmer.nl/en,
  under Linux.
  .
  Package kz is named after its creator, Karel Zimmer.
Description-nl: Installatie- en beheerscripts door Karel Zimmer
  Pakket kz bevat scripts voor het installeren en beheren van Debian en
  Debian-gebaseerde systemen zoals Ubuntu.
  .
  Zie Checklist installatie voor het gebruik van dit pakket.
  Checklist installatie is te vinden op de site https://karelzimmer.nl,
  onder Linux.
  .
  Pakket kz is vernoemd naar de maker, Karel Zimmer.
